## Product Identity Declaration

The following content in this project is designated as
Product Identity under Section 1(e) of the Open Gaming
License v1.0a and is not Open Game Content:

- All original characters, character names, and backstories
- All original locations, place names, and worldbuilding
- All original factions, organizations, and lore
- All original items, spells, abilities, and mechanics not
  derived from Open Game Content
- All artwork, maps, and visual designs created by the author

This Product Identity may not be used without explicit
permission from the author.

All Product Identity is excluded from Open Game Content.

All other content designated as Open Game Content is released
under the OGL v1.0a as described below.

---

## Open Game Content Declaration

The following content is designated as Open Game Content
under Section 1(d) of the Open Gaming License v1.0a:

- Game rules, mechanics, terminology, and stat blocks derived
  from Open Game Content
- Any files located in /public/resources/ that are marked as
  OGC or derived from OGL sources
- Any text explicitly identified as Open Game Content within
  this project

All Open Game Content is released under the terms of the
Open Gaming License v1.0a.

